# Learning Service - Final Entity Review & Class Diagram

The entities have been successfully updated to address the previous findings. The table name conflict is resolved, and Lombok usage is now consistent.

## 📊 Class Diagram

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class MainTopic {
        +Integer id
        +String name
        +String image
        +List~SubTopic~ subTopics
        +LocalDate createdAt
    }

    class SubTopic {
        +Integer id
        +String name
        +MainTopic mainTopic
        +List~Vocabulary~ vocabularies
        +LocalDate createdAt
    }

    class Vocabulary {
        +Integer id
        +String phonetic
        +String word
        +String level
        +String audioUrl
        +List~SubTopic~ subTopics
    }

    class VocabularyMeaning {
        +Integer id
